data.description: This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is the perfect place to call home! All n4 bedrooms are located on the main floor. The front living room offers lots of windows to let in natural light. Enjoy the cold winter nights in front of the fireplace. The primary bathroom is a great space with a shower, double sinks, and good under sink storage. The living space is flexible with other rooms that can be used for whatever your needs may be. Call today to take a look!!!
